name: FREEWHATSNEW10_TEXT1
value: The Child Health Center improve the lives of children, and additionally it increases the average birth rate of the city.

name: FREEWHATSNEW10_TEXT2
value: Eldercare City Services offers senior citizens a place to gather and spend time together, improving their health and thus potentially increasing the lifespans of citizens.

name: FREEWHATSNEW10_TEXT3
value: Overground Metro extends the metro functionality from underground to overground. The updated metro system will feature additional overground and elevated metro stations and a new metro train model. We've also made a lot of general improvements to the core game to make the game experience better!

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT1
value: Raise the sails and set course, it's time to go fishing with the new fishing industry addition! Manage the fishing industry all the way from fishing and fish farming to commercial products. Build harbors, plan fishing routes and protect your fish farms from harmful polluted water.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT2
value: Tourists, ahoy! A new public transport option for outside connections is here! Intercity Bus Service uses coaches to carry passengers to and from cities. Intercity Bus Service comes with a new intercity coach vehicle model and an intercity bus station.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT3
value: Much desired and highly waited feature has rolled into the city! Trolleybus is an electric bus that draws power from overhead wires using spring-loaded trolley poles. Trolleybus Service comes with various new assets, including a trolleybus depot, vehicle model and new road variations with overhead wires.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT4
value: Helicopter Service brings a new dimension to public transport. Helicopters circumvent traffic altogether and zip through the sky, connecting people in a whole new way. Helicopter Service comes with new assets: a helicopter vehicle model, a helicopter depot and helicopter stop.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT5
value: Aviation Club is a new Unique Building which increases the city's attractiveness and entertainment. Local aviation hobbyists and small plane owners can be spotted using the airfield to do recreational flying within the city's limits.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT6
value: New Transport Hubs offer multiple ways to connect your city's transport services better and more efficiently. Experiment with all the new Transport Hubs which make changing from one transport type to another easy and fast!

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT7
value: The new Waste Transfer System is an upgrade to the base game garbage service with an increase to the range of garbage services. Now players can build Waste Processing Complexes far away from their beautiful city centers and extend their service range by building smaller, less polluting Waste Transfer Facilities closer to the city center.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT8
value: Inland Water Treatment Plant extends the water services to include cities built completely inland, far away from open water sources. With Inland Water Treatment Plant, players can process waste water to completely clean water and then pump it back into circulation.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT9
value: A whole new set of policies allows you to personalize your city even more. New policies can affect city attractiveness, citizen happiness and take direct effect on preserving the environment.

name: EXPANSIONWHATSNEW10_TEXT10
value: From deserts to swamps, the five new maps provide unique vistas, new challenges and a number of exciting locations to start building your dream city.

Practise makes perfect. All players are required to attend extra practise sessions before the next match! #practise #football
Maybe having a bigger audience would cheer up our team? Everyone, come to the next match! #cometothestadium #football
LOOSERS! I'm sorry, I just meant to make it known that our team lost. What a shame! #shameonyou #shameonme #football
Do you like football? I like football! #football
I'm so happy we have a stadium in the city, I love seeing matches! #football
My kids are training to one day be professional football players, way to go! #football
Football is my favourite pasttime, I've worn out three pairs of football boots already. Costly but fun! #football
I kicked the ball so hard it flew out of the stadium. Have you seen it? #football
What a magnificent sight our team is! #football
I want to get autographs from the whole team! When is the next match? #football
I can't wait for the next match. Why can't they play every day? #football
Does anyone have a recording of the last match? I missed it! #football
I hope the next match doesn't end like the last one #football
Football fan number one here! Play more games! #football #fan1
Who wants to play football? Meet me at the park, I'll bring the ball! #football #ballbringer #parks
Our team is simply the best, win or lose. Keep on playing! #football #bestest
I've got two extra tickets to the next match, who wants to come? #tickets #football
I grew out of my football boots. Any takers? They are only gently worn! #bootswitoutahome #football
I got socks in the wrong colour accidentally. Anyone needing white and red socks? #football #freesocks #redandwhite
What a grand stadium! This will surely make the city better by all standards! #football #stadium #yay

name: MONUMENT_SHORT_DESC
value: The Unique Buildings are one of a kind buildings that will attract tourists and help you to unlock Monuments
Hello! This is Chirper. Keep an eye on what your citizens are talking about and what is happening around the world. #youfoundme
Hooray! The water pumping station has been constructed. #freshwater #mayorrocks
Fresh water will finally be running in the city. Welcome modern commodities! :) #freshwater #mayorrocks
A working #sewer system is one of the greatest #inventions in the #history of #mankind
@localnews : Mayor: ”I will celebrate the newly built drain pipe by having a hot shower”
Congratulations! The city's first power plant has been constructed. #juicedup
A local power plant is online! Maybe I'll get my TV working again. #realityshows247
I kinda like steady production of electricity but there are the environmental factors to consider. #smog
I love the smell of burning fossil-fuel in the morning! #dinopower #profossil
Hello 21th century! I'm glad the @mayor is brave enough to consider nuclear power as a valid option for electricity. #goingnuclear
Taking out the trash just became much more convenient than before. #garbage #takingoutthetrash
Turning trash into energy is a win-win situation for the city. I'm all for it. #trashistreasure
Health care for everyone! Citizens flock to get treatment for various ailments. #flushots
The city receives its first fire engines. Citizens already feel safer than before. #fireproof
@fire_department is expanding their service. Nice to see that the mayor cares for our safety. #priorities #coolmayor
The long arm of the law reaches the city. I feel safer already. #iamthelaw
The police is here to serve and protect - in a big way. #andjusticeforall
@local_government has found a place for the town hall. #forusbyus
That city hall sure is a thing to look at. Hopefully it's serves as more than just a fancy eye candy. #mayorsthrone
The importance of schooling seems to have reached the local government. #learn4life
@university citizens enroll in various courses from economics to hard sciences. #theyseemeenrolling
The bus is a great, cheap way for me to get around the city. I love it! #citizensinmotion
The citizens and the local industry thank the @mayor for the new rail network. #railroadblues
#metro - I just love it! Now I can travel to work without ever stepping above ground. #mindthegap #sweetride
Ship ahoy! Citizens celebrate the opening of the @harbor and the arrival of the first majestic ferries. #ferryspotters
Finally we have an @airport. This will get us to the great big wide world. #goinginternational
About time we got ourselves something #unique to remember our #city by. #thiscityisgreat
Now there's a building if I ever saw one. This is MONUMENTAL! #worldoftomorrow
No more urns on the mantelpiece, the new #cemetery is open!
Even though the smoke is a bit icky, a crematorium will save a lot of space in the city #ashestoashes
Honk honk, buses on the way! I'll take the bus to work, please! #citizensinmotion
Shipping outside the city just got a lot easier, it's on rails! #traincargo
Shipments can be shipped on ships. Did I say that correctly? #shiponships
Green energy is the best! I hope the mayor continues on this path of renewable energy. #greenenergy
Green energy! What an excellent choice! #greenenergy
I can already see more birds and plants in the city thanks to the use of #greenenergy
Hooray for the mayor! More #greenenergy for the city!
Citizens rejoice in the opening ceremony of the new hospital. #healthcareFTW
The new university will open even more scientific disciplines to study.
Alert, #science #geeks! The new #university is celebrating its founding by having lectures open to everyone the whole week.
Is the @mayor trying to change our city into a police state?
The new @police headquarters has #opendoors until the end of the week to celebrate its #opening. However, cell doors are still kept locked.
We have a new #firestation in the city!
I wonder why the new #firestation is not on fire already as those #firefighters in the #calendar are HOT!
I love the new parks! Thanks to the @mayor I can take my family to the park and have a nice picnic. #parksandrec
Feeling full of #energy after a #jog in the new #park
Wow! The new plaza looks really sophisticated. #lovingplazas
#Robot #invasion imminent! Check for more clues in a plaza near you. #flashmob #asimovcrew
@mayor is on a roll, building more #attractions around the city. Awesome! #moneybuyseverything
I'm happy to see my tax money being invested in the future of our city!
Our city's new #attraction will make great post cards! #proudcitizen
Our little town is not so little anymore! Great work @mayor !
Organic food: it's not just for eco-activists and hipsters anymore! #organic #veg #superfood
@public_transport aggressive ad campaign is bearing fruit and people choose public transport over their own cars. #carpool
Remember the local #daycare possibilities. #play&learn is important to developing minds. #families
My vote goes to the @mayor. Finally someone who understands what it's like to be a student. #studentlife
@local_government @mayor support the elderly and disabled. #seniors speak highly of @mayor. #manmachineinterface
Dime a dozen seems to be the new "it". Is there anywhere I can buy quality flowers? #flowers
Wow! Our town is quickly becoming a real city. #goodtimes
The @mayor is doing well leading this city. New citizens and businesses keep moving in. #flyingcolors
The city is expanding once again! On our way to becoming a #metropolis!
The @mayor has worked tirelessly, and now the regional government has passed the bill that allows for larger city territory. #annex
@mayor that's great news! #City can now annex new adjacent areas. #newpossibilities
Our city is growing and so is our #industry. I hope this is taken into account when zoning plans are made.
City limits are now officially expanded. I wonder what plans the @local_government has.
@mayor Thanks for the amazing work you have done for our city!
When is our city going to build a #school of its own?
I just signed a #petition to #build a #school in our city.
This is insane. I have to drive to the next city for a painkiller prescription or pay big bucks for a visit to a private clinic. #healthcare
Municipal healthcare is a standard in any other city of this size except ours. When are we going to get one? #21stcentury #healthcare
Our vacation was extended, could someone water the plants while we are gone. The key is in the flower pot on the porch.
@police offers small #storage spaces with secure doors for #rent. Call 911 for more information
Have you #lost your #wallet? I found a black leather wallet. Send a PM to get it back.
Looking for quality bulletproof vest for my son. Trade for some used jewelry or car stereo possible.
#Used #carstereos, #homeelectronics, #laptops and other easily movable items for sale! Fair pricing! #Delivery possible! PM for contact details.
@dailynews Several arrested in gang-related shooting. @police ask for witnesses
Before moving here I took only an #aspirin occasionally. Now I have 12 #Rxd #meds I need to take on a daily basis.
I've had a #headache for over two weeks now and painkillers are not helping. I think I should call a #doctor.
This is my third #stomachflu in three months. This is not normal, right?
What's wrong with our garbage collection service? Trash is piling up and it's swarming with flies!
Where are all the #garbage #trucks? Why is no one picking up our trash?!
I never really thought about how much garbage piles up in just two weeks.
I would think that fresh #water is basic stuff, but NO! How long do we have to wait for working water pipes?!?!
What is it with the @waterworks ?!?! #Showering with #bottledwater is getting a bit expensive.
The toilet is not working and water in the shower stinks. What's wrong with the sewers?
The streets are #flooding with #sewage. The #smell is just overwhelming.
Power to the people! How hard is it to build a working power grid? It's not exactly state-of-the-art technology.
A #blackout again? I can't even call or email the electrical company when there's no power.
Why am I living in this depressing city?
What a great city! I would think I'm dreaming if I didn't know otherwise.
Good morning everybody! What a beautiful sunrise #paradiseonearth
Congratulations to us :) @mayor just announced that our beautiful city won the "Most Attractive City" award! #happymayor
Thank you for an #amazing #vacation! See you next year!
@local_government Is the city planning to build more industry? #unemployed #welder
@dailynews Local traders and business owners request more local manufacturing industry
There's nothing to do on weekends. I would like to go shopping and eat out, but all the good places are out of town.
Three got laid off because no one was buying our factory's products. Having more local retailers would help move the stock and get our jobs back.
I'm looking for an #apartment or #house in the city. Anything will do, please PM for further contact.
@financialwatch Apartment rents are rising as the demand is high. @mayor is starting negotiations with local housing developers.
Why isn't the @local_government doing anything to stop the fires? Does anyone supervise the #firesafety #regulations at all?
My little princess was #trapped up in a #tree for 3 hrs before the #firedepartment showed up to save her majesty #savethecats #funnycats
Who should I call if no one shows up to pick up the dead? #movingout
There's a #weird #smell coming from the apartment next door. What does a #dead #person smell like?
All public services now available online! Ask your @local_government for registration instructions.
My #domestic #AI is behaving badly today. Any tips how to #comfort it and make it feel better?
Those #abandoned #houses #ruin the whole #neighborhood. Whose responsibility is it to demolish or renovate them?
I wish our city would have more parks. #bleak #gray
@mayor Closest thing to nature in this city are people's houseplants. How about a park or two?
How are my #kids supposed to play outside when this is happening? @dailynews: #Industrial #waste found in the #soil.
I dug up a barrel full of #glowing #goo in my backyard. Who should I call?
Can someone recommend good #hearing #protection? All this #noise is driving me #crazy!
Hello @mayor, ever heard about this: New #study by #scientists finds that #trees and sound barriers reduce #traffic noise.
Does your #tap #water stink? We can't even have showers because of the stench. #itsinthewater
@waterworks just told citizens not to drink tap water or take showers as microbial flora was found in the city water network. #disgusting

name: ZONING_DESC
value: Low density residential zone attracts families with children and will evolve into fancy villas.
Urban areas offer citizens apartment houses to move into. High density residential buildings attract young adults especially.
Small stores and cosy boutiques offer citizens places to spend their money. Low density commercial zones can provide the necessities for nearby low density residential areas.

High density commercial buildings are department stores and supermarkets that offer citizens a wide variety of spending possibilities. They can serve a large number of customers, so they are ideal for high density residential areas.

Industrial zones provide jobs for the citizens and produce goods for local businesses. Industry uses a lot of water and produces ground pollution to its surroundings. Be sure to place the industrial zones at a safe distance from any residential areas.
Office areas offer workplaces for educated citizens. Make sure you have a University in the city to provide suitable workers.
Release the area of any zone type. With any zoning tool selected, you can also use the secondary mouse button on a zoned area to release it.

name: UPDATEBUILDING_DESC
value: The Hot Air Balloon Tours service stores and maintains hot air balloons and organizes hot air balloon tours over the city. Tours with a high appeal value around the starting point are more popular.

The Medical Center is a research facility that works on finding cures for diseases and ailments. It is so vast and efficient that it can easily take care of all your citizens' health needs. The Medical Center has a helipad and can accept helicopters.

The Hospital treats citizens who fall ill or have an accident. Each patient takes up one bed for some time, so make sure there are enough hospitals in the city to handle all patients, otherwise city health can fall. The Hospital has a helipad and can accept helicopters.

PaulCo Industrial Steel Plant produces machine parts, tools and other industrial-grade steel products. Industrial Steel Plant needs Metals special goods for the production and packaging. Unique Factories can be placed outside Industry Area.
All Small Crop Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Medium Crop Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Large Crop Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Small Fruit Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Medium Fruit Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Large Fruit Field variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Small Animal Pastures variations require crops to produce farming special good – animal products. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.
All Large Animal Pastures variations require crops to produce farming special good – animal products. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.
All Small Crop Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Medium Crop Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Large Crop Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Small Fruit Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Medium Fruit Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
All Large Fruit Field greenhouse variations produce farming raw materials – crops. Extractor need to be placed on fertile land inside Industry Area.
Cattle sheds require crops to produce farming special good – animal products. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.
Modern slaughterhouses require crops to produce farming special good – animal products. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.
Milking parlors require crops to produce farming special good – animal products. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.

Rotary kiln use raw materials like ore and produce metals during pyroprocessing. This processing building require ore to produce ore special good – metals. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.

Glass manufacturing plants use mined ore raw materials to manufacture glass sheets. This processing building require ore to produce ore special good – glass. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.

Petrochemical plants take oil and uses fluid catalytic cracking to produce plastic. This processing building require oil to produce oil special good – plastic. Processing building need to be placed inside Industry Area.
Toll Booths collect a fee from cars passing the toll. The fee can be adjusted from the Toll Booths info panel. Cars need to stop briefly to pay the toll. No pedestrian traffic across Toll Booth.
A barn building used for storing the farming industry raw materials - crops. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A large barn building used for storing farming industry raw materials - crops. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A simple grain silo used for storing farming industry raw materials – crops. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A large grain silo used for storing farming industry raw materials – crops. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A single oil pump for extracting oil industry raw material from an underground reservoir. Extractor need to be placed on oil field inside Industry Area.
A line of four oil pumps for extracting oil industry raw materials from an underground reservoir. Extractor need to be placed on oil field inside Industry Area.
A small oil drilling rig for extracting oil industry raw materials from an underground reservoir. Extractor need to be placed on oil field inside Industry Area.
A large oil drilling rig for extracting oil industry raw materials from an underground reservoir. Extractor need to be placed on oil field inside Industry Area.
An Offshore Oil Drilling Platform for extracting oil industry raw materials from seabed deep rock formations. Extractor need to be placed on oil field inside Industry Area.
A small crude oil storage with pumping station, pipes and four tanks for storing oil industry raw materials. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A large crude oil storage with pumping station, pipes, eight tanks and small maintenance building for storing oil industry raw materials. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A fenced field with a pumping station and other equipment that is used to pump oil raw materials to large underground oil storage caverns. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
Two dome shelters for storing oil industry raw materials. Storage building can be placed outside Industry Area.
A small mine for extracting ore industry area raw materials from underground deposits. Extractor need to be placed on ore deposit inside Industry Area.
A large mine with advanced equipment for extracting ore industry area raw materials from underground deposits. Extractor need to be placed on ore deposit inside Industry Area.
A mining vessel designed to extract ore industry area raw materials from underwater deposits. Extractor need to be placed on ore deposit inside Industry Area.

name: UPDATEBUILDING_SHORT_DESC
value: The Medical Center provides healthcare for the whole city. The Medical Center has a helipad and can accept helicopters.
The hospital treats patients with any diseases or injury. The Hospital has a helipad and can accept helicopters.
PaulCo Industrial Steel Plant produces industrial-grade steel products and requires Metals for the production and packaging.

name: UPDATELEVELUP_SPECIAL_INDUSTRY
value: Specialized buildings are always of the highest level.

name: UPDATEDDISASTERWARNING
value: Astronomers tell of an asteroid named [XXX] coming dangerously close and will land on the area.

name: UPDATEPARADOX_ACCOUNT_CONNECT_LABEL
value: Connect Paradox account to Steam account

name: UPDATEPDX_STEAM_ERRORMESSAGE
value: Request to Steam services timed out. Make sure you are logged in on Steam and running Steam client in online mode.
Request to Steam services timed out. Make sure you are logged in on Steam and running Steam client in online mode.
Seems that your Steam account hasn’t been connected to any Paradox Plaza account yet. You can connect the accounts after logging in with your Paradox Plaza account.

name: UPDATEPARADOX_ACCOUNT_INCENTIVE
value: Log in or create a Paradox Account and receive the Paradox Plaza for free!

name: UPDATEINDUSTRYPANEL_EFFICIENCY_TOOLTIP
value: The efficiency bonus makes Extractors and Processing Buildings in the area process resources faster.

name: UPDATEINDUSTRYPANEL_POLLUTION_TOOLTIP
value: The higher the industry level, the less pollution is caused by Extractors and Processing Buildings in it.

name: UPDATEBUDGET_INFO
value: A higher budget increases Extractors, Processing Buildings and Unique Factories production rate as well as allow them to house more vehicles.

name: UPDATEFREEWHATSNEW8_TEXT1
value: Build road tolls to add an extra payment for going to certain areas. Traffic driving through the toll must slow down at the booths and pay a fee. Ticket price can be adjusted with a slider. New Automated Toll city policy makes passing the toll booths faster but with reduced income.

name: UPDATEEXPANSIONWHATSNEW8_TEXT1
value: Create Industry Areas with new tool and determine the Industry Area type with four new Main Buildings. Main Buildings allow level progression and work as a headquarter for city services. Level up the areas to unlock new buildings and features.

name: UPDATETUTORIAL_ADVISER
value:
Industry Areas can be created by new tool. Main Building determines type of area. Industry Areas need raw materials, like Oil, to operate. Materials can either be imported or gathered by Extractors. Areas can fully operate on imported raw materials only.

Raw materials can be exported, sold to specialized industry or used by Processing buildings. Processing buildings produce special goods, which can be either exported, sold to non-specialized industry or used by Unique Factories.

Unique Factories produce Luxury Goods, which can be exported or sold to commercial zones.

Industry Areas can be created by new tool. Main Building determines type of area. Industry Areas need raw materials, like Oil, to operate. Materials can either be imported or gathered by Extractors. Areas can fully operate on imported raw materials only.

Raw materials can be exported, sold to specialized industry or used by Processing buildings. Processing buildings produce special goods, which can be either exported, sold to non-specialized industry or used by Unique Factories.

Unique Factories produce Luxury Goods, which can be exported or sold to commercial zones.

name: UPDATEPOLICIES_DETAIL
value:
Allow zoned industry to work even more effectively by overlooking a few work safety laws. 
- Doubles the amount of goods produced by zoned industry buildings
- Upkeep: 6 ₡ / zoned industrial building
Zoned industrial buildings need to filter their waste, making them pollute the ground a lot less. Cost 2 ₡/ zoned industrial building / week

name: UPDATENOTIFICATION_NORMAL
value:
Low amount of special goods available.
Make sure trucks carrying them from processing buildings can reach the Unique Factory.

If the missing resource is produced in a far away place, building a warehouse storing it nearby can help ensure that there is always some available.

name: UPDATEDBUILDING_DESC
value: Public Library is a cultural institution, which collects and stores books, films, newspapers, documents and much more. Everything is now made accessible to all citizens around the city for borrowing. Library gives a small bonus to education within building radius.

name: UPDATEDPOLICIES_DETAIL
value:
The new technologies alter the nature of the industrial workforce.
- All industrial workplaces are for well- and highly educated citizens
- Increased production output by 50%
- Reduces workplaces by 30% / zoned industry

All education facilities become for-profit and students are required to pay tuition fees to attend school. 
- Education building upkeep -50%
- Cost: Reduces citizens happiness

The local Public Libraries organize a book fair.
- Increased happiness and entertainment within the Public Libraries radius
- Cost: Public Libraries upkeep increased by 100%

Students are provided with free healthcare by the campus.
- Increases student health
- Cost: Campus upkeep cost increases by 5₡ / student

Students are provided with meal vouchers which they can use in the campus cafeteria to get a free lunch.
- Increases student happiness
- Cost: Campus upkeep cost increases by 1₡ / student.

The campus hires various lecturers and scholars to teach on the campus. Affects all faculties within the campus area
- Increases Faculty bonus +25%
- Cost: Increases Faculty upkeep by 25%

The varsity team gives out free fan merchandise to the fans during matches and organizes fan club trips to away matches.
- Increases the odds of winning home and away matches by 7%.
- Cost: 400₡ / week

Advertise the Varsity Sports matches throughout the city to have more visitors on the arenas.
- Increase amount of visitors to the arenas by 20%
- Cost: 200₡ / week / arena located on campus

The varsity team has become famous! City businesses are offering to sponsor the local team.
- Decreased upkeep cost of campus' varsity sports by 8%.
- Billboard change from varsity team's logo to sponsor's brand

Make your parks and plazas the envy of the country! 
- Moderately increased Land Value around parks and plazas
- Increases the Parks and Plazas budget by 20%

name: UPDATEDACH_DESC
value: Have 30 000 students studying on campuses at the same time.
Build all five varsity sports arenas on one campus in one city.
Cover one campus are upkeep cost entirely with tuition fees paid by students after all of the campus buildings and faculties are built.
Build all Campus Area types with all of their respective campus buildings and faculties.
Build five Offshore Oil Drilling Platforms.
Answer to everything in a numeric form.

name: UPDATE_FREEWHATSNEW9_TEXT1
value: The Public Library is an education building that provides a small chance for citizens to gain an education whenever they visit it. For those who take an advantage of the Public Library City service there is also new Unique Building called Academic Library to unlock.
